#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; clicks the mouse whenever the mouse cursor pauses briefly. It "
"was designed to help those with repetitive strain injuries, for whom "
"pressing buttons hurts. It can also drag the mouse, although this takes a "
"bit more practice."
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; klikne mišem kad god kursor miša se zaustavi na kratko. "
"Osmišljeno je kako bi pomoglo ljudima sa povredama prstiju. Takođe možete "
"povući miš ali za to je potrebno više prakse."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; can eliminate the pain caused by clicking the mouse, and helps "
"many people to use the computer without pain. Unfortunately, some pain can "
"also be caused by simply moving the mouse around the table. If you are "
"experiencing computer-related pain and haven't yet seen a doctor, please do "
"so."
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; može eliminirati bol uzrokon klikanjem miša i pomaže mnogim "
"ljudima da bezbolno koriste račinar. Nažalost neka bol može biti uzrokovana "
"povlačenjem miša po stolu. Ukoliko imate slične bolove i niste posjetili "
"doktora, molimo Vas da to učinite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Just to make it absolutely clear: while &kmousetool; can help reduce the "
"pain caused by <emphasis>clicking</emphasis> the mouse, it cannot help any "
"pain caused by <emphasis>moving</emphasis> the mouse. And, like all "
"ergonomic tools, your mileage may vary."
msgstr ""
"Samo da bude sasvim jasno: sve dok &kmousetool; može umanjiti bol uzrokovan "
"<emphasis>klikanjem</emphasis> miša, ali ne moće umanjiti bol uzrokovan "
"<emphasis>pomjeranjem</emphasis> miša. I kao kod svih ergonomskih pomagala, "
"vaša mileage? može varirati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kmousetool;"
msgstr "Korištenje &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &kmousetool; is simple: &kmousetool; watches as you move the mouse, "
"and when you pause briefly, it clicks."
msgstr ""
"Korištenje &kmousetool; je jednostavno: &kmousetool; prati vaše kretnje mipa "
"i kada se zaustavite, on klikne."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool;'s Smart Drag mode allows you to drag the mouse."
msgstr "&kmousetool; Smart Drag vam omogućava da povlačite mišem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Smart Drag is enabled, &kmousetool; pauses after it clicks down; if you "
"move the mouse, it waits until you stop moving before it clicks up. This "
"way, you can both click and drag the mouse. Smart Drag takes a bit more "
"practice, but becomes natural once you get used to it."
msgstr ""
"Kada je Smart Drag uključen &kmousetool; zastaje nakon što klikne, ako "
"pomjerite miš, čeka da se zaustavi prije nego što klikne. Na ovaj način "
"možete kliknuti i povlačiti mip. Smart Drag zahtjeva malo više prakse ali "
"postaje prirodan kada se na njega naviknete."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Upute za naredbe"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Main &kmousetool; window"
msgstr "Glavni &kmousetool; prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool;'s options are accessed mostly via the mouse."
msgstr "&kmousetool; opcije su dostupne preko miša."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Start</guibutton>/<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Start</guibutton>/<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts (or stops) &kmousetool;."
msgstr "Startuje (ili stopira) &kmousetool;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Minimum movement:"
msgstr "Minimalni pokret:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The minimum movement in pixels before &kmousetool; will attempt to click the "
"mouse."
msgstr "Minimalni pokret u pikselima prije nego &kmousetool; pokuša da klikne."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dwell time (1/10 sec):"
msgstr "Vrijeme sadržaja (1/10 sec):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The time the mouse has to pause before &kmousetool; clicks. Try increasing "
"this time if it is hard getting used to &kmousetool;"
msgstr ""
"Vrijeme koje miš mora pauzirati prije nego &kmousetool; klikne. Probajte "
"povećati ovo vrijeme ako se teško navići na &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Smart drag"
msgstr "Pametno povlačenje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enables or disables Smart Drag. Disabled use is easier, so this is the "
"default."
msgstr ""
"Uključuje ili iskljuluje Smart Drag. Fabrički je ova opcija isključena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable <guilabel>Smart drag</guilabel> the <guilabel>Drag time (1/10 "
"sec):</guilabel> field becomes available. This is the time &kmousetool; "
"waits, after it clicks down, before it clicks back up if you don't move the "
"mouse."
msgstr ""
"Ako uključite <guilabel>Smart drag</guilabel> <guilabel>Vrijeme povlačenja "
"(1/10 sec):</guilabel> polje postaje aktivno. To je vrijeme koje "
"&kmousetool; čeka prije nego klikne ako ne pomjerate miš."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable strokes"
msgstr "Uklučiti poteze"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmousetool; now supports strokes. When you enable strokes, a slow move to "
"the right and back, followed by a pause, will generate a <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click. A slow move left and back will generate a double click. "
"(Strokes are specified in <filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/"
"kmousetool_strokes.txt</filename>. This file is generated by &kmousetool; "
"the first time it is run, but can be modified afterwards.)"
msgstr ""
"&kmousetool; sada podržava poteze. Kada uključite ovu opciju, spori potez "
"mišem udesno i nazad, sa pauzom između, generisat će <mousebutton>desni</"
"mousebutton> klik. Spori potez lijevo generisat če dvostruki lijevi klik. "
"(Potezi su specificirani u <filename>$<envar>KDEHOME</envar>/share/config/"
"kmousetool_strokes.txt</filename>. Ovaj fajl je generisan od &kmousetool; "
"kada se prvi put pokrene ali se može modifikovati.)"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Audible click"
msgstr "Zvučni klik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:165
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Plays a sound when &kmousetool; clicks down. This helps, especially with "
"Smart Drag."
msgstr ""
"Odsvira zvuk kada &kmousetool; klikne. Ovo pomože, posebno sa Smart Drag."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with desktop session"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is enabled, &kmousetool; will start each time the session of the "
"desktop starts."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid "Defaults"
msgstr "Podrazumijevano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset all settings to their defaults."
msgstr "Resetuje sve postavke na podrazumjevane."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reset"
msgstr "Reset"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reset all settings to their state when you opened the dialog, or, if you "
"have already saved a setting with the <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> button, "
"reset all settings to the state when you last pressed <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>"
msgstr ""
"Resetuje sve postavke na njihovo stanje kada se otvori dijalog ili ako već "
"imate spašene postavke sa <guibutton>Apply</guibutton> dugmetom, resetuje "
"postavke na vrijeme kada ste zadnji put pritisnuli <guibutton>Apply</"
"guibutton>"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid "Apply"
msgstr "Primijeni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid "After changing any settings, you must click this button."
msgstr "Nakon bilo koje promjene postavke, morate kliknuti ovo dugme."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:202
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help"
msgstr "Pomoć"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the User manual (this document)."
msgstr "Otvara pomoć korisnicima (ovaj dokument)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close"
msgstr "Zatvorite"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close the dialog without saving any settings."
msgstr "Zatvori dijalog bez spašavanje postavki."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit"
msgstr "Izlaz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &kmousetool;"
msgstr "Napusti &kmousetool;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips"
msgstr "Savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "These tips can help shorten &kmousetool;'s learning curve a bit."
msgstr "Ovi savjeti mogu pomoći da lakše savladate &kmousetool;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can modify the time delays &kmousetool; waits, for both clicking and for "
"dragging."
msgstr ""
"Možete modifikovati vrijeme odgađanja koje &kmousetool; čeka, i za klik i za "
"povlačenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's best to practice clicking with &kmousetool; using its defaults first. "
"You may especially want to leave Smart Drag disabled at first. Then, once "
"you are comfortable clicking, move on to practicing Smart Drag."
msgstr ""
"Najbolja vježba klikanja sa &kmousetool; je koristeći podrazumjevane "
"postavke. Ostavite Smart Drag isključen na početku. Onda, kada uvježbate "
"klikanje, možete mastaviti sa vježbanjem Smart Drag-a."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "When using Smart Drag, it may help to enable the Audible Click"
msgstr "Kada koristite Smart Drag, može vam pomoći ako uključite zvučni klik."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using the Audible Click, you may need to speed up &kde;'s audio "
"response."
msgstr ""
"Kada koristite zvučni klik, možda ćete trebati ubrzati &kde;audio odgovor."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Questions and Answers"
msgstr "Pitanja i Odgovori"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid "Help! &kmousetool; keeps dropping spurious clicks all over the screen!"
msgstr "Pomoć! &kmousetool; upotreljava lažne klikove svuda po ekranu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are using &kmousetool;, you do have to learn new mousing habits."
msgstr ""
"Kada koristite &kmousetool;, morate se naučiti novim navikama ovog miša."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, keep in mind where it's safe to click &mdash; clicking on gray parts "
"of windows or non-link areas of web browsers won't hurt anything, so you can "
"safely rest the mouse over those areas until you need it."
msgstr ""
"Prvo, umajte na umu gdje je sigurno da se klikne &mdash; klikanje na sivi "
"dio prozora ili ne-linkovane oblasti web pretraživača neće ništa pokvariti, "
"pa moćete možete odmoriti mip na ovim prostorima sve dok ga ponovo ne "
"zatrebate."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Second, you need to know where you're going to click before you move the "
"mouse. Most of the time, when we know we're going to use the mouse, most of "
"us grab the mouse and start moving it around randomly until we figure out "
"where we want to click. With &kmousetool;, you need to know where you're "
"going to click before you move the mouse in the first place. It is also a "
"good idea to keep your hands off the mouse when you're not using it."
msgstr ""
"Drugo, trebate znati gdje ćete kliknuti kada pomjerite miša. Većinu vremena, "
"kada znamo da ćemo koristiti miša, većina nas uhvati miša i počne ga "
"slučajno pomijerati dok se ne zaključi  gdje se treba kliknuti. Sa "
"&kmousetool;, treba znati gdje treba  kliknuti prije nego se uopšte koristi "
"miš. Dobra je ideja skloniti ruke od miša kada se on ne koristi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "My mouse sticks when I move it. Can I still use &kmousetool;?"
msgstr ""
"Moj miš se lijepa kada je u pokretu. Mogu li i dalje koristit &kmousetool;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. If your mouse sticks, it means you need to clean your mouse. This is "
"usually easy to do; the trick is that you have to clean not just the mouse's "
"ball, but the rollers that the ball rolls against inside the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Da. Ako vam se miš lijepi, to znači da ga morate očistiti. To je obično lako "
"uraditi; ne samo da morate očistiti kuglu miša nego i unutrašnje valjke koje "
"okreće kugla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, you have to remove the ball. The method for doing this varies from "
"mouse to mouse, but it's usually pretty clear how to do this if you look at "
"the bottom of the mouse."
msgstr ""
"Prvo uklonite kuglu. Kako to uraditi varira od miša do miša, ali obično vam "
"bude jasno kako se to radi ukoliko pogledate u dno miša."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you've removed the ball, you should be able to see the rollers on the "
"sides of the hole that contained the ball. The dirt and grime on them can be "
"easily scraped off with a flat blade or with a fingernail."
msgstr ""
"Kada uklonite kuglu, trebali bi ste vidjeti valjke na stranama rupe u kojoj "
"je bila kugla. Prašina sa njih se lako skida nekom oštricom ili noktom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool; clicks down and never clicks up. What's happening?"
msgstr "&kmousetool; klikne ali nikad ne otpusti klik. Šta se dešava?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:297
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some rare situations, the system suspends &kmousetool; when a drag "
"starts; if you are using Smart Drag, this means that &kmousetool; can never "
"finish the drag by clicking up."
msgstr ""
"U nekim rijetkim situacijama, sistem suspendira &kmousetool; ako poveče miš, "
"ako koristite Smart Drag, to znači da &kmousetool; neće nikad završiti "
"povlačenje sa otpuštanjem klika miša."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This happens when you use &kmousetool; under a non &kde; window manager and "
"then use it to move a window."
msgstr ""
"Ovo se dešava kada koristite &kmousetool; bez &kde; prozor menađera i onda "
"ga koristite da pomjerate prozor."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The solution is to simply click manually; this resets &kmousetool;, and you "
"can then continue to work normally again."
msgstr ""
"Rješenje je da kliknete ručno, to će resetovati &kmousetool;, i onda možete "
"normalno nastaviti sa korištenjem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmousetool; moves the cursor when I am trying to type."
msgstr "&kmousetool; pomjera kursor kada ja pokušavam da pišem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Problem: When you're typing text, &kmousetool; keeps dropping clicks and "
"moving the cursor away from where you want to type."
msgstr ""
"Problem: kada ja pišem tekse &kmousetool; sam klika i pomjera kursor sa "
"prostora gdje želim kucati."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Solution: Use the mouse to place the cursor where you want it, but when "
"you're ready to type, park the mouse on a neutral area on the screen. Then, "
"if you bump the mouse, or if it moves a few pixels, any random clicks that "
"it sends won't matter. Safe places to park the mouse include the gray areas "
"around toolbars and menus, and on the title bars of windows."
msgstr ""
"Rješenje: Koristite miš da pozicionirate kursor gdje želite da bude, ali "
"kada krenete sa kucanjem, pomjerite miš na neutralni prosotr ekrana. Onda, "
"ako pomjerite miš nekoliko piksela, bilo koji slučajni klik neće smetati "
"vašem kucanju. Sigurna mjesta za pozicioniranje miša su sive podloge po "
"toolbar-ima i menijima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I'm trying to use Smart Drag, but I cannot get the hang of using it to edit "
"text."
msgstr ""
"Pokušavam koristiti Smart Drag ali ne mogu skontati kako ga korisititi za "
"editovanje teksta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Smart Drag is an advanced feature of &kmousetool;, and takes some getting "
"used to. It is very possible to use it to select text, to cut and paste, and "
"use it in almost any situation where you would normally want to drag the "
"mouse. But you probably won't be able to do this at first. Here are some "
"suggestions:"
msgstr ""
"Pametno prevlačenje je napredna mogućnost &kmousetool;, i zahtijeva nešto "
"navikavanja. Često je moguće koristiti ga za izbor teksta, isijecanje i "
"umetanj, i koristiti ga u skoro svakoj situaciji u kojoj biste željeli "
"prevući miša. Ali to vjerovatno nećete moći inicijalno uraditi. Ovdje su "
"date neke sugestije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Don't use Smart Drag while you are first learning to use &kmousetool;. "
"Instead, to select text, click at one end of the text, and hold down the "
"shift key while you click at the other end of the text."
msgstr ""
"Nemojte koristiti Smart Drag kada učite koristiti &kmousetool;. Umjesto "
"selektovanje teksta, kliknite na početakteksta i držite shift tipku  kad "
"kliknete na kraj teksta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the Audible Click. This will play a <quote>click</quote> sound when "
"&kmousetool; clicks down, and this will tell you when the Smart Drag delay "
"is beginning. With practice, you can use Smart Drag without the Audible "
"Click, but it does take a fair amount of practice."
msgstr ""
"Koristite zvučni klik. Ovo će odsvirati <quote>click</quote> zvuk "
"kada&kmousetool; klikne, i ovo će vam reći kada Smart Drag odgaća svoj "
"početak. Sa vježbom možete koristiti Smart Drag bez zvučnog klika ali za to "
"će trebati mnogo vježbe."

